ItemBGDesc: A vegetable salad that was once sold at an astounding price, believed to bring good luck and happiness to those who consumed it. Later, a chef replaced the expensive clover with regular lettuce, making it an affordable dish for the masses.\n\n"But now, it no longer brings anyone happiness."
